title: Excavation for alleged buried treasure concludes without findings
byline: The excavation in search of alleged buried treasure near the Central Expressway construction site in the Wanduramba area of Veyangoda ended yesterday evening without any discovery of treasure or items of archaeological value.

title: Prez Dissanayake must fully implement ’vision document’ with India: Wickremesinghe
byline: Former Sri Lankan President Ranil Wickremesinghe said his successor Anura Kumara Dissanayake should fully implement the “vision document” adopted with India last year.
